^B@2^*Bhondo717: ^*N|cp||at|In general, with an 11 card fit missing the king, the odds slightly favor the drop over the finesse. But on this hand there is a more important reason. Don has to get rid of the a heart loser. If he takes the spade finesse and it loses, he will lose 1 heart and a spade. But by playing the @SA he guarantees the contract because he can pitch his 2 heart losers on the clubs and diamonds. |
